<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Eloy website</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg-start: #31363b;
        --bg-end: #1f2224;
        --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        --muted: #dbe6f0;
        --accent: #6ea8ff;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial;
        background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 10% 10%, var(--bg-start) 0%, var(--bg-end) 60%);
        color: var(--muted);
        margin: 0;
        -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
      }

      h1 {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.01));
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 16px;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.6px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
      }

      p {
        background: var(--card);
        color: var(--muted);
        text-align: left;
        padding: 22px;
        margin: 0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
        font-size: 1.03rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      h2 { color: #fff; margin: 0 0 0 0; }

      .main {
        display: flex;
        gap: 48px;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 8px 20px 28px;
        max-width: 1040px;
        margin: 8px auto 20px;
      }

      .main .left { flex: 1 1 60%; }

      .main .right {
        flex: 0 0 320px; 
        max-width: 320px;
        margin-left: auto; 
        margin-right: 0;
        align-self: flex-start;
      }

      .left .invite-card { margin-top: 16px; }

      h2.features {
        position: relative;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(110,168,255,0.06), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
        padding: 22px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.55), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
        border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);
        color:#fff;
        transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease;
      }

      h2.features::after {
        content: "";
        position:absolute;
        left:10%;
        right:10%;
        top:8%;
        height:34%;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.35), rgba(255,255,255,0));
        transform: skewY(-3deg);
        opacity:0.85;
        border-radius:6px;
        pointer-events:none;
      }

      h2.features:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 26px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);}

      .right h2 ul { margin: 10px 0 0 20px; padding: 0; }

      .main a { color: aliceblue; text-decoration: underline; }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .main { flex-direction: column; }
        .main .right, .main .left { max-width: 100%; }
      }

    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Eloy Browser</h1>

    <div class="main">
      <div class="left">
        <p>
          Why choose Eloy? Eloy Browser, created by Tekalu and br34thless, is built for speed, simplicity, and full user control. It’s lightweight, responsive, and free from unnecessary clutter, while still giving you all the essential features. Privacy and customization are at its heart, offering transparency and freedom that many other browsers don’t. With passionate developers continuously improving it, Eloy is more than a browser—it’s a modern, user-focused tool designed for people who value performance, clean design, and a browser that actually listens.
        </p>

        <div class="invite-card">
          <strong>Join our Discord</strong>
          <div style="margin-top:8px;">
            <a href="https://discord.gg/ZhFMZXXB" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://discord.gg/ZhFMZXXB</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="right">
        <h2 class="features">
          Whats included?
          <ul>
            <li>Adblocker</li>
            <li>Memberships</li>
            <li>Secure browsing</li>
            <li>Fast performance</li>
          </ul>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>